Let me give you the flavor of the Hack. Jay Mohr, who starred with Hackett in ACTION back in 1999, tells the following storyÃƒÂ¢?Ã‚Â¦


I was sick off my ass with the flu, and the phone rings. Its Hackett. I pick up the phone
Hiya pal! You dont sound too good. I called to see how you are?

Im not well. I got the flu, Im pissed off, I got no sleep, I have wake up to do radio spots for a show thats already sold out, my back hurts..

Well, slow down. Whenever I dont feel so good, I always try to remind myself of the Siamese twin whose brother is gay, whose boyfriend is coming over, and they share the same a--hole.


You are going to be memorizing jokes from this one, trust me.
